Zubrin, Robert. FIRST LANDING. New York: Ace Books, [2001]. Octavo, boards. First edition. The author's first novel. An account of Earth's first manned mission to Mars. "A Ken Follett-like Mars novels ... with the ring of authority." - Gregory Benford. Publisher's publicity sheet laid in. A fine copy in fine dust jacket. (#104022).
